198const GcnBufferFormatInfo *getGfx10PlusBufferFormatInfo(uint8_t BitsPerComp, uint8_t NumComponents, uint8_t NumFormat) {
199 struct KeyType {
200 uint8_t BitsPerComp;
201 uint8_t NumComponents;
202 uint8_t NumFormat;
203 };
204 KeyType Key = {BitsPerComp, NumComponents, NumFormat};
205 auto Table = makeArrayRef(Gfx10PlusBufferFormat);
206 auto Idx = std::lower_bound(Table.begin(), Table.end(), Key,
207 [](const GcnBufferFormatInfo &LHS, const KeyType &RHS) {
208 if (LHS.BitsPerComp < RHS.BitsPerComp)
209 return true;
210 if (LHS.BitsPerComp > RHS.BitsPerComp)
211 return false;
212 if (LHS.NumComponents < RHS.NumComponents)
213 return true;
214 if (LHS.NumComponents > RHS.NumComponents)
215 return false;
216 if (LHS.NumFormat < RHS.NumFormat)
217 return true;
218 if (LHS.NumFormat > RHS.NumFormat)
219 return false;
220 return false;
221 });
222
223 if (Idx == Table.end() ||
224 Key.BitsPerComp != Idx->BitsPerComp ||
225 Key.NumComponents != Idx->NumComponents ||
226 Key.NumFormat != Idx->NumFormat)
227 return nullptr;
228 return &*Idx;
229}

958
959const ImageDimIntrinsicInfo *getImageDimIntrinsicInfo(unsigned Intr) {
960 if ((Intr < Intrinsic::amdgcn_image_atomic_add_1d) ||
961 (Intr > Intrinsic::amdgcn_image_store_mip_cube))
962 return nullptr;
963
964 struct KeyType {
965 unsigned Intr;
966 };
967 KeyType Key = {Intr};
968 auto Table = makeArrayRef(ImageDimIntrinsicTable);
969 auto Idx = std::lower_bound(Table.begin(), Table.end(), Key,
970 [](const ImageDimIntrinsicInfo &LHS, const KeyType &RHS) {
971 if (LHS.Intr < RHS.Intr)
972 return true;
973 if (LHS.Intr > RHS.Intr)
974 return false;
975 return false;
976 });
977
978 if (Idx == Table.end() ||
979 Key.Intr != Idx->Intr)
980 return nullptr;
981 return &*Idx;
982}

1456 { IMAGE_STORE_MIP, AMDGPUDimCube, 465 },
1457 };
1458
1459 struct KeyType {
1460 unsigned BaseOpcode;
1461 unsigned Dim;
1462 };
1463 KeyType Key = {BaseOpcode, Dim};
1464 auto Table = makeArrayRef(Index);
1465 auto Idx = std::lower_bound(Table.begin(), Table.end(), Key,
1466 [](const IndexType &LHS, const KeyType &RHS) {
1467 if ((unsigned)LHS.BaseOpcode < (unsigned)RHS.BaseOpcode)
1468 return true;
1469 if ((unsigned)LHS.BaseOpcode > (unsigned)RHS.BaseOpcode)
1470 return false;
1471 if ((unsigned)LHS.Dim < (unsigned)RHS.Dim)
1472 return true;
1473 if ((unsigned)LHS.Dim > (unsigned)RHS.Dim)
1474 return false;
1475 return false;
1476 });
1477
1478 if (Idx == Table.end() ||
1479 Key.BaseOpcode != Idx->BaseOpcode ||
1480 Key.Dim != Idx->Dim)
1481 return nullptr;
1482 return &ImageDimIntrinsicTable[Idx->_index];
1483}

1635const MIMGDimInfo *getMIMGDimInfoByAsmSuffix(StringRef AsmSuffix) {
1636 struct IndexType {
1637 const char * AsmSuffix;
1638 unsigned _index;
1639 };
1640 static const struct IndexType Index[] = {
1641 { "1D", 0 },
1642 { "1D_ARRAY", 1 },
1643 { "2D", 2 },
1644 { "2D_ARRAY", 3 },
1645 { "2D_MSAA", 5 },
1646 { "2D_MSAA_ARRAY", 4 },
1647 { "3D", 6 },
1648 { "CUBE", 7 },
1649 };
1650
1651 struct KeyType {
1652 std::string AsmSuffix;
1653 };
1654 KeyType Key = {AsmSuffix.upper()};
1655 auto Table = makeArrayRef(Index);
1656 auto Idx = std::lower_bound(Table.begin(), Table.end(), Key,
1657 [](const IndexType &LHS, const KeyType &RHS) {
1658 int CmpAsmSuffix = StringRef(LHS.AsmSuffix).compare(RHS.AsmSuffix);
1659 if (CmpAsmSuffix < 0) return true;
1660 if (CmpAsmSuffix > 0) return false;
1661 return false;
1662 });
1663
1664 if (Idx == Table.end() ||
1665 Key.AsmSuffix != Idx->AsmSuffix)
1666 return nullptr;
1667 return &MIMGDimInfoTable[Idx->_index];
1668}
1669
1670const MIMGDimInfo *getMIMGDimInfoByEncoding(uint8_t Encoding) {
1671 struct IndexType {
1672 uint8_t Encoding;
1673 unsigned _index;
1674 };
1675 static const struct IndexType Index[] = {
1676 { 0x0, 0 },
1677 { 0x1, 2 },
1678 { 0x2, 6 },
1679 { 0x3, 7 },
1680 { 0x4, 1 },
1681 { 0x5, 3 },
1682 { 0x6, 5 },
1683 { 0x7, 4 },
1684 };
1685
1686 auto Table = makeArrayRef(Index);
1687 size_t Idx = Encoding;
1688 return Idx >= Table.size() ? nullptr : &MIMGDimInfoTable[Table[Idx]._index];
1689}
1690#endif

1716const MIMGG16MappingInfo *getMIMGG16MappingInfo(unsigned G) {
1717 struct KeyType {
1718 unsigned G;
1719 };
1720 KeyType Key = {G};
1721 auto Table = makeArrayRef(MIMGG16MappingTable);
1722 auto Idx = std::lower_bound(Table.begin(), Table.end(), Key,
1723 [](const MIMGG16MappingInfo &LHS, const KeyType &RHS) {
1724 if ((unsigned)LHS.G < (unsigned)RHS.G)
1725 return true;
1726 if ((unsigned)LHS.G > (unsigned)RHS.G)
1727 return false;
1728 return false;
1729 });
1730
1731 if (Idx == Table.end() ||
1732 Key.G != Idx->G)
1733 return nullptr;
1734 return &*Idx;
1735}

7158
7159const MIMGInfo *getMIMGOpcodeHelper(unsigned BaseOpcode, unsigned MIMGEncoding, uint8_t VDataDwords, uint8_t VAddrDwords) {
7160 struct KeyType {
7161 unsigned BaseOpcode;
7162 unsigned MIMGEncoding;
7163 uint8_t VDataDwords;
7164 uint8_t VAddrDwords;
7165 };
7166 KeyType Key = {BaseOpcode, MIMGEncoding, VDataDwords, VAddrDwords};
7167 auto Table = makeArrayRef(MIMGInfoTable);
7168 auto Idx = std::lower_bound(Table.begin(), Table.end(), Key,
7169 [](const MIMGInfo &LHS, const KeyType &RHS) {
7170 if ((unsigned)LHS.BaseOpcode < (unsigned)RHS.BaseOpcode)
7171 return true;
7172 if ((unsigned)LHS.BaseOpcode > (unsigned)RHS.BaseOpcode)
7173 return false;
7174 if ((unsigned)LHS.MIMGEncoding < (unsigned)RHS.MIMGEncoding)
7175 return true;
7176 if ((unsigned)LHS.MIMGEncoding > (unsigned)RHS.MIMGEncoding)
7177 return false;
7178 if (LHS.VDataDwords < RHS.VDataDwords)
7179 return true;
7180 if (LHS.VDataDwords > RHS.VDataDwords)
7181 return false;
7182 if (LHS.VAddrDwords < RHS.VAddrDwords)
7183 return true;
7184 if (LHS.VAddrDwords > RHS.VAddrDwords)
7185 return false;
7186 return false;
7187 });
7188
7189 if (Idx == Table.end() ||
7190 Key.BaseOpcode != Idx->BaseOpcode ||
7191 Key.MIMGEncoding != Idx->MIMGEncoding ||
7192 Key.VDataDwords != Idx->VDataDwords ||
7193 Key.VAddrDwords != Idx->VAddrDwords)
7194 return nullptr;
7195 return &*Idx;
7196}

12624 [](const IndexType &LHS, const KeyType &RHS) {
12625 if (LHS.Opcode < RHS.Opcode)
12626 return true;
12627 if (LHS.Opcode > RHS.Opcode)
12628 return false;
12629 return false;
12630 });
12631
12632 if (Idx == Table.end() ||
12633 Key.Opcode != Idx->Opcode)
12634 return nullptr;
12635 return &MIMGInfoTable[Idx->_index];
12636}

12934
12935const MTBUFInfo *getMTBUFOpcodeHelper(unsigned Opcode) {
12936 struct KeyType {
12937 unsigned Opcode;
12938 };
12939 KeyType Key = {Opcode};
12940 auto Table = makeArrayRef(MTBUFInfoTable);
12941 auto Idx = std::lower_bound(Table.begin(), Table.end(), Key,
12942 [](const MTBUFInfo &LHS, const KeyType &RHS) {
12943 if (LHS.Opcode < RHS.Opcode)
12944 return true;
12945 if (LHS.Opcode > RHS.Opcode)
12946 return false;
12947 return false;
12948 });
12949
12950 if (Idx == Table.end() ||
12951 Key.Opcode != Idx->Opcode)
12952 return nullptr;
12953 return &*Idx;
12954}

13177 { TBUFFER_STORE_FORMAT_X_OFFSET_exact, 0x3, 197 },
13178 { TBUFFER_STORE_FORMAT_X_OFFSET_exact, 0x4, 188 },
13179 };
13180
13181 struct KeyType {
13182 unsigned BaseOpcode;
13183 uint8_t elements;
13184 };
13185 KeyType Key = {BaseOpcode, elements};
13186 auto Table = makeArrayRef(Index);
13187 auto Idx = std::lower_bound(Table.begin(), Table.end(), Key,
13188 [](const IndexType &LHS, const KeyType &RHS) {
13189 if (LHS.BaseOpcode < RHS.BaseOpcode)
13190 return true;
13191 if (LHS.BaseOpcode > RHS.BaseOpcode)
13192 return false;
13193 if (LHS.elements < RHS.elements)
13194 return true;
13195 if (LHS.elements > RHS.elements)
13196 return false;
13197 return false;
13198 });
13199
13200 if (Idx == Table.end() ||
13201 Key.BaseOpcode != Idx->BaseOpcode ||
13202 Key.elements != Idx->elements)
13203 return nullptr;
13204 return &MTBUFInfoTable[Idx->_index];
13205}

13430
13431 struct KeyType {
13432 unsigned Opcode;
13433 };
13434 KeyType Key = {Opcode};
13435 auto Table = makeArrayRef(Index);
13436 auto Idx = std::lower_bound(Table.begin(), Table.end(), Key,
13437 [](const IndexType &LHS, const KeyType &RHS) {
13438 if (LHS.Opcode < RHS.Opcode)
13439 return true;
13440 if (LHS.Opcode > RHS.Opcode)
13441 return false;
13442 return false;
13443 });
13444
13445 if (Idx == Table.end() ||
13446 Key.Opcode != Idx->Opcode)
13447 return nullptr;
13448 return &MTBUFInfoTable[Idx->_index];
13449}
13450#endif

14315
14316const MUBUFInfo *getMUBUFOpcodeHelper(unsigned Opcode) {
14317 struct KeyType {
14318 unsigned Opcode;
14319 };
14320 KeyType Key = {Opcode};
14321 auto Table = makeArrayRef(MUBUFInfoTable);
14322 auto Idx = std::lower_bound(Table.begin(), Table.end(), Key,
14323 [](const MUBUFInfo &LHS, const KeyType &RHS) {
14324 if (LHS.Opcode < RHS.Opcode)
14325 return true;
14326 if (LHS.Opcode > RHS.Opcode)
14327 return false;
14328 return false;
14329 });
14330
14331 if (Idx == Table.end() ||
14332 Key.Opcode != Idx->Opcode)
14333 return nullptr;
14334 return &*Idx;
14335}

15194 { BUFFER_STORE_SHORT_OFFSET_exact, 0x1, 850 },
15195 { BUFFER_WBINVL1, 0x0, 851 },
15196 { BUFFER_WBINVL1_SC, 0x0, 852 },
15197 { BUFFER_WBINVL1_VOL, 0x0, 853 },
15198 };
15199
15200 struct KeyType {
15201 unsigned BaseOpcode;
15202 uint8_t elements;
15203 };
15204 KeyType Key = {BaseOpcode, elements};
15205 auto Table = makeArrayRef(Index);
15206 auto Idx = std::lower_bound(Table.begin(), Table.end(), Key,
15207 [](const IndexType &LHS, const KeyType &RHS) {
15208 if (LHS.BaseOpcode < RHS.BaseOpcode)
15209 return true;
15210 if (LHS.BaseOpcode > RHS.BaseOpcode)
15211 return false;
15212 if (LHS.elements < RHS.elements)
15213 return true;
15214 if (LHS.elements > RHS.elements)
15215 return false;
15216 return false;
15217 });
15218
15219 if (Idx == Table.end() ||
15220 Key.BaseOpcode != Idx->BaseOpcode ||
15221 Key.elements != Idx->elements)
15222 return nullptr;
15223 return &MUBUFInfoTable[Idx->_index];
15224}

16087
16088 struct KeyType {
16089 unsigned Opcode;
16090 };
16091 KeyType Key = {Opcode};
16092 auto Table = makeArrayRef(Index);
16093 auto Idx = std::lower_bound(Table.begin(), Table.end(), Key,
16094 [](const IndexType &LHS, const KeyType &RHS) {
16095 if (LHS.Opcode < RHS.Opcode)
16096 return true;
16097 if (LHS.Opcode > RHS.Opcode)
16098 return false;
16099 return false;
16100 });
16101
16102 if (Idx == Table.end() ||
16103 Key.Opcode != Idx->Opcode)
16104 return nullptr;
16105 return &MUBUFInfoTable[Idx->_index];
16106}
16107#endif

16642
16643const RsrcIntrinsic *lookupRsrcIntrinsic(unsigned Intr) {
16644 struct KeyType {
16645 unsigned Intr;
16646 };
16647 KeyType Key = {Intr};
16648 auto Table = makeArrayRef(RsrcIntrinsics);
16649 auto Idx = std::lower_bound(Table.begin(), Table.end(), Key,
16650 [](const RsrcIntrinsic &LHS, const KeyType &RHS) {
16651 if (LHS.Intr < RHS.Intr)
16652 return true;
16653 if (LHS.Intr > RHS.Intr)
16654 return false;
16655 return false;
16656 });
16657
16658 if (Idx == Table.end() ||
16659 Key.Intr != Idx->Intr)
16660 return nullptr;
16661 return &*Idx;
16662}
16663#endif

17237
17238const SMInfo *getSMEMOpcodeHelper(unsigned Opcode) {
17239 struct KeyType {
17240 unsigned Opcode;
17241 };
17242 KeyType Key = {Opcode};
17243 auto Table = makeArrayRef(SMInfoTable);
17244 auto Idx = std::lower_bound(Table.begin(), Table.end(), Key,
17245 [](const SMInfo &LHS, const KeyType &RHS) {
17246 if (LHS.Opcode < RHS.Opcode)
17247 return true;
17248 if (LHS.Opcode > RHS.Opcode)
17249 return false;
17250 return false;
17251 });
17252
17253 if (Idx == Table.end() ||
17254 Key.Opcode != Idx->Opcode)
17255 return nullptr;
17256 return &*Idx;
17257}
17258#endif

17465const SourceOfDivergence *lookupSourceOfDivergence(unsigned Intr) {
17466 struct KeyType {
17467 unsigned Intr;
17468 };
17469 KeyType Key = {Intr};
17470 auto Table = makeArrayRef(SourcesOfDivergence);
17471 auto Idx = std::lower_bound(Table.begin(), Table.end(), Key,
17472 [](const SourceOfDivergence &LHS, const KeyType &RHS) {
17473 if (LHS.Intr < RHS.Intr)
17474 return true;
17475 if (LHS.Intr > RHS.Intr)
17476 return false;
17477 return false;
17478 });
17479
17480 if (Idx == Table.end() ||
17481 Key.Intr != Idx->Intr)
17482 return nullptr;
17483 return &*Idx;
17484}
